CatDescriptText: image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 27, 1962, pg. 13, reads: "Homewood 'Y' - Among those persons at the annual banquet at the Homewood YMCA were, first row, left to right: Rev. and Mrs. LeRoy K. Patrick; second row, Mrs. Robert Smith, Rev. J.A. Williams, Rev. J.M.F. Brown, and Mrs. Dollie Douglas, and third row, Lawrence Priestly, Roscoe Fleming, and Dace McEachern. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Rev. and Mrs. K. Leroy Patrick seated at table with Mrs. Robert Smith, Rev. J. A. Williams, Rev. J. M. F. Brown, and Dollie Douglas standing directly behind and back row, Lawrence Priestly, Roscoe Fleming, and Dace McEachern, most wearing cowboy hats, gathered behind table for Homewood YMCA annual banquet with signs inscribed "Join the Y Now It's Round Up Time!", "Dude", "Quota Buster", and "Top Hand Honor Roll"
